{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "mtpx-websocket-chat-collection",
    "name": "mtpx websocket chat",
    "description": "Postman collection for the Multpex WebSocket Chat example.\n\nThis example demonstrates:\n- WebSocket-based real-time chat\n- Room management\n- Message history\n- Typing indicators\n\n## WebSocket Endpoints\n\nWebSocket connections should be made to:\n```\nws://{{baseUrl}}/ws/chat?token={{authToken}}\n```\n\n### WebSocket Events (send)\n\n| Event | Payload | Description |\n|-------|---------|-------------|\n| `chat.join` | `{ roomId: string }` | Join a chat room |\n| `chat.leave` | `{ roomId: string }` | Leave a chat room |\n| `chat.send` | `{ roomId: string, content: string }` | Send a message |\n| `chat.typing` | `{ roomId: string, isTyping: boolean }` | Typing indicator |\n| `chat.history` | `{ roomId: string, limit?: number, before?: string }` | Get message history |\n| `chat.rooms` | `{}` | Get list of joined rooms |\n\n### WebSocket Events (receive)\n\n| Event | Payload | Description |\n|-------|---------|-------------|\n| `chat.message` | `{ roomId, userId, content, timestamp }` | New message in room |\n| `chat.typing` | `{ roomId, userId, isTyping }` | User typing status |\n| `chat.user.joined` | `{ roomId, userId }` | User joined room |\n| `chat.user.left` | `{ roomId, userId }` | User left room |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{authToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "roomId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Basic health check endpoint."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Readiness Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/ready",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "ready"]
            },
            "description": "Readiness check - verifies all dependencies are connected."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Liveness Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/live",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "live"]
            },
            "description": "Liveness check - verifies service is running."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Rooms",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Rooms",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('List rooms returns 200', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response is array', function() {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/rooms",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "rooms"]
            },
            "description": "Lista todas as salas de chat disponíveis. Requer autenticação."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Room",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('roomId', response.id);",
                  "        console.log('Room ID saved:', response.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Room created successfully', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has room id', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(response).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(response).to.have.property('name');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"General Chat\",\n  \"description\": \"A room for general discussions\",\n  \"type\": \"public\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/rooms",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "rooms"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new chat room.\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `name` (required): Room name (2-100 chars)\n- `description` (optional): Room description (max 500 chars)\n- `type` (optional): 'public' or 'private' (default: 'private')"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Room",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Room retrieved successfully', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has room details', function() {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(response).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(response).to.have.property('name');",
                  "    pm.expect(response).to.have.property('type');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/chat/rooms/{{roomId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["chat", "rooms", "{{roomId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Get details of a specific room.\n\nRequires authentication. For private rooms, user must be a member."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "WebSocket Examples",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "WebSocket Connection Info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/ws/chat",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["ws", "chat"]
            },
            "description": "# WebSocket Connection\n\nThis is a placeholder to document the WebSocket endpoint.\n\n**Connection URL:**\n```\nws://localhost:3000/ws/chat?token=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN\n```\n\n**Authentication:**\nPass the JWT token as a query parameter `token`.\n\n## Example Messages\n\n### Join Room\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"chat.join\",\n  \"data\": { \"roomId\": \"room-uuid\" }\n}\n```\n\n### Send Message\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"chat.send\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"roomId\": \"room-uuid\",\n    \"content\": \"Hello, world!\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Typing Indicator\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"chat.typing\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"roomId\": \"room-uuid\",\n    \"isTyping\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Get History\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"chat.history\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"roomId\": \"room-uuid\",\n    \"limit\": 50\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Leave Room\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"chat.leave\",\n  \"data\": { \"roomId\": \"room-uuid\" }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
